{"tid":2487534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國: 中國是最大的威脅, 先於俄羅斯","createTime":"2021-04-13T15:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T16:34:02.000Z","uid":134071,"like":126,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"515b206f11948f1db9a9d16cd16a39bb201acc05","tid":2487534,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"美國政府既情報機關, 剛發表最新報告, 排名列出最大威脅: 中國排第一, 其次是俄羅斯, 伊朗, 北韓.<br />\n<br />\nChina poses the biggest threat to the U.S., a new intelligence report says.<br />\nBy Julian E. Barnes<br />\n<br />\n    April 13, 2021, 10:45 a.m. ET<br />\n<br />\nChina&rsquo;s effort to expand its growing influence represents one of the largest threats to the United States, according to a major annual intelligence report released on Tuesday, which also warned that Beijing was capable of cyberattacks that could temporarily disrupt critical infrastructure in the United States.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>The report puts China&rsquo;s push for &ldquo;global power&rdquo; first on the list of threats, followed by Russia, Iran and North Korea. </strong>There are typically few broad revelations in the annual reports, which are a collection of declassified assessments, although the intelligence agencies&rsquo; ranking of threats and how they change over time can be telling.<br />\n......<br />\n&ldquo;The American people should know as much as possible about the threats facing our nation and what their intelligence agencies are doing to protect them,&rdquo; said Avril B. Haines, the director of national intelligence, whose office released the report.<br />\n<br />\nThe new report will be followed by congressional testimony by Ms. Haines; William J. Burns, the C.I.A. director; and other top intelligence officials on Wednesday and Thursday."},{"pid":"e2e41fb6ca1a4d35597a3a6b1181704cc2df8f2e","tid":2487534,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"515b206f11948f1db9a9d16cd16a39bb201acc05","tid":2487534,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"美國政府既情報機關, 剛發表最新報告, 排名列出最大威脅: 中國排第一, 其次是俄羅斯, 伊朗, 北韓.<br />\n<br />\nChina poses the biggest threat to the U.S., a new intelligence report says.<br />\nBy Julian E. Barnes<br />\n<br />\n    April 13, 2021, 10:45 a.m. ET<br />\n<br />\nChina&rsquo;s effort to expand its growing influence represents one of the largest threats to the United States, according to a major annual intelligence report released on Tuesday, which also warned that Beijing was capable of cyberattacks that could temporarily disrupt critical infrastructure in the United States.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>The report puts China&rsquo;s push for &ldquo;global power&rdquo; first on the list of threats, followed by Russia, Iran and North Korea. </strong>There are typically few broad revelations in the annual reports, which are a collection of declassified assessments, although the intelligence agencies&rsquo; ranking of threats and how they change over time can be telling.<br />\n......<br />\n&ldquo;The American people should know as much as possible about the threats facing our nation and what their intelligence agencies are doing to protect them,&rdquo; said Avril B. Haines, the director of national intelligence, whose office released the report.<br />\n<br />\nThe new report will be followed by congressional testimony by Ms. Haines; William J. Burns, the C.I.A. director; and other top intelligence officials on Wednesday and Thursday."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/13/us/politics/us-threat-assessment-china.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2021%2F04%2F13%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fus-threat-assessment-china.html&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=fbf19678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/13/us/politics/us-threat-assessment-china.html</a>"},{"pid":"fff4589482851ccbf1b